  "detailed_description": "I got a little plane. I call it Cannoship. I with my cannonship fight strange enemies to save the world<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313120/extras/5a81876bbc99446399c32ba6d37c8ebe.poster.avif?t=1665311470\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313120/extras/5a81876bbc99446399c32ba6d37c8ebe.webm?t=1665311470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313120/extras/5a81876bbc99446399c32ba6d37c8ebe.mp4?t=1665311470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Overview:</strong><br>Cannon ship is a classic shooter game but with modern touches! <br>You must fight with huge number of enemies to save the world from annihilation. You don't seem to stand a chance, but by upgrade your ship you can destroy a bosses and many different enemies! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313120/extras/2cb35c3b32bc203153b93d7a105c4bb3.poster.avif?t=1665311470\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313120/extras/2cb35c3b32bc203153b93d7a105c4bb3.webm?t=1665311470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313120/extras/2cb35c3b32bc203153b93d7a105c4bb3.mp4?t=1665311470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br>- 8 different sceneries<br>- single player or local cooperation mode<br>- upgrade your airship<br>- achievements<br>- support for game controllers<br>- pixel art<br>- retro difficulty level<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313120/extras/5fcfb21ae4a7cdb07a948abdffdf274b.poster.avif?t=1665311470\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313120/extras/5fcfb21ae4a7cdb07a948abdffdf274b.webm?t=1665311470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313120/extras/5fcfb21ae4a7cdb07a948abdffdf274b.mp4?t=1665311470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Cannonship is a game created by one person with only two hands :)",
